ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Avidity Calibrator Controls: 
1 Bottle (6.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Avidity Calibrator containing phosphate buffered saline.
2 Bottles (6.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Avidity Control: Low avidity control and High avidity control.
ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Avidity Reagent kit, 100 tests (50 avidity determinations):
Microparticles: 1 Bottle (6.6 mL) Recombinant Toxoplasma gondii antigen coated microparticles in MES buffer.
Conjugate: 1 Bottle (5.9 mL) Murine acridinium-labeled anti-human IgG in MES buffer.
Assay Diluent: 1 Bottle (10.0 mL) Toxo IgG assay diluent containing TRIS buffer.
Pre-treatment 1: 1Bottle (2.9 mL) Pre-treatment reagent 1 containing MES buffer.
Pre-treatment 2: 1Bottle (2.9 mL) Pre-treatment reagent 2 containing blocking agent in MES buffer.
